Author: Lud12
Title: [ANN][WISEPLAT] - 💎💎💎 THE NEXT GENERATION BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM ✅
Body: SCALABILITY Using several blockchains becomes the solution for the scalability problem for Bitcoin and other blockchains, for instance, Ethereum.  The idea is to ensure a stable payments channel along the first blockchain and record the intermediate application transaction in separate blockchains for each individual app.  For instance, using the second blockchain a user can find an app which solves his/her tasks. Let’s assume that it is some digital content. Then the provider of the digital content and its consumer will reflect their cash flow for the content in the first blockchain, and will store the transactions leading to payment in the application blockchain. By using such an architecture, the platform can adjust to a rate of a thousand transactions per second.  Join us https://oswiseplat.org  #scalability #blockchain #cryptocurrency #bitcoin #ethereum #wiseplat #wise #preico #ico

Author: Lud12
Title: [ANN][WISEPLAT] - 💎💎💎 THE NEXT GENERATION BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM ✅
Body: Hello!  Thank you!  Right you are! 2 main blockchains and private blockchains for individual applications:  Blockchain WISEPLAT operates not with one blockchain, but with two main blockchains and a lot of blockchains for individual applications. The first blockchain is for operations with WISE tokens (fast transactions, PoW), the second blockchain is for the application catalog with lockout WISE in favor of application users (scaling, DPoS / PoW). This separation allows WISEPLAT to conduct fast transactions with WISE tokens and provide effective scalability for applications.

Title: [ANN][WISEPLAT] - 💎💎💎 THE NEXT GENERATION BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM ✅
Body: Hello, Lirik! Our Road Map consist from 5 steps:  January-February 2018 - The minimum test environment will be prepared. March-April 2018 - We are moving to full test environment. May-June 2018 - We are doing massive Testing & Security Audit. July-August 2018 - Doing the optimization of current systems. September-October 2018 - All nodes going into to Production Clusters and then we can start application development.  WISEPLAT platform will be ready.

Title: [ANN][WISEPLAT] - 💎💎💎 THE NEXT GENERATION BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM ✅
Body: We think that our platform WISEPLAT gives more for opportunities.  If you take the Windows operating system, then it is a common platform for different applications. The same is for WISEPLAT, it is a common platform for various blockchain applications.   Besides, we allow interaction between different blockchain applications among themselves, in particular through smart contracts.  The existence of such an architecture does not exclude all the opportunities as in Ethereum platform, as example.

Author: Lud12
Title: [ANN][WISEPLAT] - 💎💎💎 THE NEXT GENERATION BLOCKCHAIN SYSTEM ✅
Body: The main concepts of our project are highlighed here:  The goals of the WISEPLAT project  SPEED EXECUTION Blockchain WISEPLAT operates not with one blockchain, but with two main blockchains and a lot of blockchains for individual applications. The first blockchain is for operations with WISE tokens (fast transactions, PoW), the second blockchain is for the application catalog with lockout WISE in favor of application users (scaling, DPoS / PoW). This separation allows WISEPLAT to conduct fast transactions with WISE tokens and provide effective scalability for applications.  SCALABILITY Using multiple blockchains allows the blockchain system WISEPLAT to easily scale under increasing loads.  REMOVE THE LIMITATIONS OF SMART CONTRACTS WISEPLAT allows the creation of smart contracts that will exchange data with external data sources, which greatly expands the capabilities of blockchain applications. Contracts can be executed between different blockchains.  ANONYMOUS ACCOUNTS + CONFIRMATION BY THE OWNER Using the account verification system will allow users for their accounts by their own get the status of identifiable accounts.  TRUST WISEPLAT implements the APP Store for its blockchain applications. The use of rating assessments of the application allows users to quickly and safely in most cases choose the application.
